content: SELECT user_info.web_user_info.user_yandex_uid, event_type, object_info.offerInfo.offer_id, client_info.client_type, FROM hahn.`home/verticals/broker/prod/warehouse/realty/event/1d/#DATE#` where user_info.web_user_info.user_yandex_uid = '#YANDEX_UID#' and event_type in ("CARD_SHOW", "PHONE_SHOW") order by event_type desc;
